response.original_title: IMPACT Wrestling x AAA: Ultra Clash 2023
response.overview: AAA/Impact Wrestling Ultra Clash was a Special Event produced by TNA / Impact Wrestling and Lucha Libre AAA Worldwide, which took place on November 26, 2023, at the ShowCenter Complex in San Pedro Garza García, Nuevo León, Mexico.  The main event of the show was Motor City Machine Guns (Alex Shelley & Chris Sabin) & El Hijo del Vikingo vs. Trey Miguel & Los Vipers (Latigo & Toxin).
